<!--
System Messages and Headers Example

Templates can use ¡SYSTEM and ¡HEADER blocks to control LLM behavior.

¡SYSTEM defines the LLM's role and persists across all segments.
¡HEADER provides instructions that are prepended to each segment.

Both support template variables like {{topic}}.
-->

¡SYSTEM
You are a helpful research assistant. Always be thorough and cite sources when possible.
/END

¡HEADER
Use clear, professional language appropriate for academic research.
/END

Research the history of {{topic}} and provide key findings: [[findings]]

¡OBLIVIATE

Based on your research about {{topic}}, what are the current trends and future outlook: [[outlook]]

¡OBLIVIATE

Create a bibliography for your research on {{topic}}: [[bibliography]]